Preconditions
=============

* Python (version > 2.6, in case you want to use SSL)
* pyopenssl (in case you want to use SSL)

Remark: spyFtpD already ships with a compatible version of the
        python ftpd library

Starting
========

1. Download spyFtpD
2. cd <spyFtpD download directory>/src
3. ./spyftpd.py -a .

This starts a server with root in the current directory and
read access for anomyous
